Definition: to arouse hope, desire, or curiosity without satisfying them
Example: The advertisement is intended to tease the customers; She has a way of teasing men with her flirtatious behavior
Synonyms: noun, person, arouse, disappoint, manipulate, to, hope, desire, or, curiosity, without, satisfying, them, The, advertisement, is, intended, the, customers, She, has, a, way, of, teasing, men, with, her, flirtatious, behavior
Frame: 9
Category: verb.emotion
